{"tid":869701,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我小學果陣激到個老師發火","createTime":"2018-10-20T13:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T13:34:45.000Z","uid":123335,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28aa96fe9ee4c1906332a6067c59f426841da4e9","tid":869701,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"果個老師教英文<br />\n但好衰格<br />\n成日話我地班同學個腦係「豆腐」<br />\n話：「你地係咪冇腦架？ 就算冇都用你個豆腐諗下野啦」<br />\n<br />\n之後我就玩野<br />\n上堂果陣不斷細細聲重覆老師講野<br />\nEg 個老師話「Take out your book and turn to page 10」<br />\n我就細細聲照copy 佢呢句野 <br />\n<br />\n我copy 佢講野兩堂之後<br />\n就忍唔住好嬲咁的左我去後樓梯講野<br />\n話「你知唔知你咁樣重覆我講野好冇禮貌？」<br />\n我話「我想學好d 英文渣」<br />\n激到佢痴線 <br />\n最尾搞到我要見校長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93a248553ab2a45ab113a65b66cfbbf6d46b0b5","tid":869701,"uid":76098,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:30:31.000Z","msg":"的去後樓梯個陣嚇到瀨尿個part又唔提"},{"pid":"f23e5d031636d155a7ef57ba77587395e0df2f23","tid":869701,"uid":180124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:31:15.000Z","msg":"小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞咁多野最後都係比老師玩7"},{"pid":"fbbbc3e2b75a2e702061d6e7e2ffc681e0d9b6de","tid":869701,"uid":111271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"淨係講野都要去後樓梯?"},{"pid":"8d27678a40dbe1dbb5472b03fdce4ddc2d7f49cb","tid":869701,"uid":189605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:32:30.000Z","msg":"叻"},{"pid":"8c3fb565f0fb215a827c441ad6b570aae8bd369d","tid":869701,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"中學個陣唔記得左做咩搞到個miss推左我一野<br />\n校長知道左之後冇耐個miss就話病左唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}